{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_03_03",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "まったくもう……\nみんな、こんなに靴を散らかしちゃって……",
      "startTime": 2.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "元気なのはいいですけど\nちょっと元気が有り余っているようですね",
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "もっと練習メニューを増やしてもらえるよう\n{user}さんにお話ししてみようかしら",
      "startTime": 13.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……沙季？\n玄関の掃除をしてくれてたのか、ありがとう",
      "startTime": 19.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "はい。綺麗にしないとやっぱり落ち着かなくて",
      "startTime": 23.4366894086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに手伝ってもらった方がいいんじゃないか\nなんなら俺が手伝うよ",
      "startTime": 31.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "いいんです。私が好きでやっていることですから",
      "startTime": 33.4573921521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私が『自分を貫く』といえば\nやっぱりこれだなって思いました",
      "startTime": 41.2906572978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "夜中に何か食べたら、走りに行かないとダメって\nソワソワしてしまうし",
      "startTime": 47.2906572978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "料理も、手を抜いたら自分に負けた気がして\n……自分らしくないことをしてもダメですね",
      "startTime": 55.0906572978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さん……\n少しいいでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 62.3906572978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、どうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 64.7573239644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "あれから、ずっと考えていたんです",
      "startTime": 67.1426527579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "自分を貫くのが大切、というのは分かったんですけど\nでは、その自分……私とは一体なんなのでしょう",
      "startTime": 75.5426527579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスのような特技もありませんし\n強い自己主張がある訳でもありません",
      "startTime": 84.2426527579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり私には、真面目にやってきたことくらいしか\nみんなに胸を張れることがなくて……",
      "startTime": 91.5675208438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "うん、俺も真面目なのが沙季らしさだと思う\nちゃんと自分で自分のことを分かってるじゃないか",
      "startTime": 99.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　そんなことが、私らしさ……？\n本当に、それでいいんでしょうか……？",
      "startTime": 108.1933100621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "とても大事なことだと思う\n沙季は誰よりも真摯にステージに向き合ってるよ",
      "startTime": 114.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 117.5466432809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "段取りやバミの位置だって、直前まで\nミスがないように確認してるのを、俺は知ってるよ",
      "startTime": 123.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、それでは\nただ真面目っていうだけです、よね？",
      "startTime": 129.8039677858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "情熱が伝わらなければ、今までと変わらない……\n弾けていない……というのがそもそもの問題ですから",
      "startTime": 137.0373245001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "……あ。『伝わらない』……伝えるためには……\n私を見てもらわないと……いけない？",
      "startTime": 147.1373011191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（どうやら自分で何かを掴んだようだな）",
      "startTime": 150.9706344525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "そのために……私がアイドルを頑張ってる理由を\nさらけ出す……？",
      "startTime": 158.534858028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "だったら後は、どこでどうやってさらけ出すか、だな\n来週、月ストのライブがあるんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 166.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "……確かに、直接お客さんに私の声を届けられる\n一番の場所ですもんね。私、やってみます！",
      "startTime": 174.0799771229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "countdownstage"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後。ライブイベント当日",
      "startTime": 179.6133104562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "countdownstage"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "countdownstage"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "初めまして！　私達、月のテンペストです！",
      "startTime": 184.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.333333400026,
          "startTime": 187.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_03_03-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "さっそくですけど、私達の自己紹介をかねて\nメンバーへの質問コーナーにいきましょう",
      "startTime": 192.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
